                <h1>Adrien Brody: Oscar-Winning Actor & Hollywood Icon</h1>
                <p>Adrien Brody is a renowned American actor born on April 14, 1973, celebrated for his intense performances and versatility. He gained fame for his role in "The Pianist," earning an Academy Award at just 29, making him the youngest actor to win Best Actor. Brody continues to captivate audiences with his compelling work across film and television.</p>
